  "body": "### Description\r\nAs a future user of the Artemis client, I want the `ChainStorageServer` class to be implemented in several ways that will allow state to be stored in different protocols. \r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n* An interface that will be sufficient to store data to arbitrary protocols\r\n* An `ChainStoreServer` that sends data to the disk to be stored\r\n* An `ChainStoreServer` that sends data to be stored in IPFS.\r\n* [Optional] A subclass is created that sends data to a git repository to be stored. \r\n",
